 Mercy Aigbe has joined her colleagues to condemn the actions of Baba Ijese over the rape allegations leveled against him asking that he’s brought to book. Mercy Aigbe in a post on her Instagram page said there’s no peace for a rapist hence Baba Ijesha should be brought to book praying that God protects all children from the hands of these rapists who hide themselves. View this post on Instagram A post shared by MERCY AIGBE (@realmercyaigbe)